data.description: Ask your agent for a copy of the full upgrade list in the supplements! Potential to assume their VA Loan at 4.25%! Impeccably renovated residence with a fusion of contemporary living and an enchanting backyard paradise. New Roof, Impact windows and upgrades galore such as April 22, a new garage door motor and MyQ smart garage door system, enhancing functionality and convenience. May 22 brought privacy fencing around the inviting pool. June 22 saw a remarkable landscape transformation with the introduction of rock accents, a center island, and lush greenery. A comprehensive renovation, covering various areas like the living room, hallway, office, guest bathroom, master bedroom, master closet, and master bathroom. Fresh paint, new doors, vanities, and modern fixtures uplifted the entire home. In Oct 22, a captivating rock wall and electric LED fireplace transformed the living room, complemented by new hardware, curtain rods, and lighting fixtures. Dec 22 brought the new roof Outdoor improvements included a privacy solar lights, fresh pool cage screens and doors. May 23 saw sprinkler and pool timer upgrades. X flood zone and 2040 expected date for UEP hookups, a ton of peace of mind.
